---
    import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
    import AlertAddCar from '../../components/AlertAddCar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Little Nightmares III | Game Cave">
    <main>
        <section class="overflow-hidden bg-bg">
            <div class="container px-5 py-12 mx-auto">
                <div class="lg:w-4/5 mx-auto flex flex-wrap">
                    <img alt="ecommerce" class="lg:w-[35%] w-full object-cover object-center rounded-md article-thumb-img" src="/articles/littlenightmares3.jpg">
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full lg:pl-10 lg:py-6 mt-6 lg:mt-0" id="article" data-article-id="4">
                        <h1 class="text-white text-3xl title-font font-medium mb-1 article--name">Little Nightmares III</h1>
                        <div class="flex mb-4">
                            <span class="flex items-center">
                                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span class="text-primary-200 ml-3">0 Reseñas</span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="leading-relaxed text-txt-200">Embárcate en una nueva aventura en el inigualable mundo de Little Nightmares. En Little Nightmares III, acompañarás a Low y Alone mientras buscan la forma de escapar de la Nada. Los dos amigos, atrapados en la Espiral, un conglomerado de perturbadoras ubicaciones, deberán cooperar para sobrevivir en un peligroso mundo lleno de ilusiones y escapar de las garras de un mal aún mayor que se oculta en las sombras. Por primera vez en la franquicia, afronta los miedos de tu infancia junto a un amigo en el modo cooperativo en línea o en solitario con una IA acompañante.</p>
                        <div class="flex mt-5">
                            <span class="font-medium text-2xl text-txt-200">$899</span>
                            <button class="flex ml-auto text-white bg-xbox border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-accent-200 rounded-md duration-500" type="submit" id="add-to-cart">Agregar al carrito</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <AlertAddCar/>
    </main>
</Layout>